            "reponse": "in order to / so as to"
          },
          {
            "numero": "1.b",
            "texte": "The teacher explained the lesson again __________ make sure everybody understood.",
            "niveau": "easy",
            "reponse": "in order to / so as to"
          },
          {
            "numero": "1.c",
            "texte": "He woke up very early __________ miss the bus to Yaound\u00E9.",
