      {
        "numero": 2,
        "texte": "Reliez les deux phrases pour former une seule phrase exprimant le but. Utilisez \u0022in order to\u0022 ou \u0022so as to\u0022.",
        "niveau": "medium",
        "reponse": "Voir les sous-questions",
        "sousQuestions": [
          {
            "numero": "2.a",
            "texte": "She studies hard every evening. She wants to get a scholarship for the university.",
